{"tid":2406451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"十大富豪之一 FB 朱克伯格 在俄羅斯「被申請破產」","createTime":"2021-02-13T08:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T10:26:47.000Z","uid":25468,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f267a742d8668af8c95ac029544936a42932df","tid":2406451,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hQyMhnO1BDlZwERgXfohxAUpHDTlDfR1VFCdfSS9_UGFcIk4BTiUVYFMTWWdUcUkIHiVFMVcUFWcIJkoDHCQV/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hQyMhnO1BDlZwERgXfohxAUpHDTlDfR1VFCdfSS9_UGFcIk4BTiUVYFMTWWdUcUkIHiVFMVcUFWcIJkoDHCQV%2Fw1200&h=362f7c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯衛星通訊社今日（11日）報導，全球十大富豪排行榜第四位的 Facebook 行政總裁朱克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）在俄羅斯申請破產，當地通訊社在法庭索引中，發現他近日向莫斯科仲裁法院遞交破產申請昨日登記在冊，申請交由當地法官拉麗薩▪克拉夫丘科處理。不過，任何人都可以申請破產，不需要在申請前就著其身份證實破產，所有材料會在申請之後才作確認。<br />\n<br />\n當地通訊社法庭索引中發現其申請昨日登記在冊 ，Facebook和其朱克伯格並沒有透露其他事宜，難以說明箇中原因。最令人匪夷所思的是， 2020年，馬克&middot;扎克伯格以939億美元財富排名2020年福布斯全球十大富豪排行榜第四位，難以想像會破產。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/v2/article/MG36Bz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fv2%2Farticle%2FMG36Bz&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=4db95384\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/v2/article/MG36Bz</a>"},{"pid":"a6561d3fee2c7e29176e637f7100f03c4dec1305","tid":2406451,"uid":281306,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haNSf4P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaNSf4P.jpg&h=fb53eff8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pogWHKR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpogWHKR.jpg&h=5db46be3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EXGLA4S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEXGLA4S.jpg&h=8288156a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.